            <h4>üìã Toronto STR Regulations (2025)</h4>
            <ul>
              <li><strong>Registration Required:</strong> All STR operators must register with the City of Toronto</li>
              <li><strong>Principal Residence Rule:</strong> You can only STR your principal residence (where you live)</li>
              <li><strong>180-Night Cap:</strong> Maximum 180 nights per year if you're away during the rental</li>
              <li><strong>No Cap:</strong> Unlimited nights if you remain in the home during guest stays</li>
              <li><strong>4% Municipal Tax:</strong> Must collect and remit Municipal Accommodation Tax</li>
